@startuml Inheritance_Flow
!theme plain

title How Data Flows Through Inheritance

|Protected Inheritance|
start
:Base has protected data;
:Middle inherits protected;
note right: data becomes protected in Middle
:GrandChild inherits public;
note right: data stays protected
#lightgreen:GrandChild CAN access data;
stop

|Private Inheritance|
start
:Base has protected data;
:Middle inherits private;
note right: data becomes private in Middle
:GrandChild inherits public;
note right: data is hidden (private in Middle)
#pink:GrandChild CANNOT access data;
stop

@enduml